{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Safari has a powerful new interface for designing responsive web experiences. Explore this great new feature and other new capabilities and improvements to the Web Inspector—WebKit’s built-in development tool. Discover how you can use Safari and Web Inspector to powerfully and efficiently design, debug, and optimize for the web."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Related Sessions","anchor":"Related-Sessions"},{"type":"links","style":"list","items":["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC16-420-Optimizing-Web-Content-in-Your-App"]}],"kind":"content"}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2015\/505\/","isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","type":"reference"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC15-505-Using-Safari-to-Deliver-and-Debug-a-Responsive-Web-Design","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc15-505-using-safari-to-deliver-and-debug-a-responsive-web-design"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC15"]]},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"WWDC15","title":"Using Safari to Deliver and Debug a Responsive Web Design","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Not